and 
<specimenCount pageId="10" pageNumber="219" type="female">6 ♀♀</specimenCount>
<quantity box="[891,1037,211,234]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.12" metricValueMax="4.72" metricValueMin="3.52" pageId="10" pageNumber="219" unit="mm" value="41.2" valueMax="47.2" valueMin="35.2">35.2–47.2 mm</quantity>
, as percentage of SL: predorsal length (31.6) 28.9–32.0; preanal length (55.1) 52.4–56.6; dorsalfin base (74.3) 65.0–76.1; anal-fin base (38.8) 36.3–40.8; pelvic-fin length (20.0) 20.4–22.8; caudal-fin length (21.5) 19.8–22.8; depth at anal-fin origin (15.0) 12.5–16.2; head length (32.7) 29.8–32.6; orbit diameter (8.3) 8.1–9.3; upper jaw length (25.9) 20.4–24.5 ƋƋ, 19.0–21.1 
<specimenCount box="[1372,1417,387,411]" pageId="10" pageNumber="219" type="female">♀♀</specimenCount>
. As percentage of head length: postorbital head length (68.9) 65.2–68.4; upper jaw length (79.1) 65.2–78.9 ƋƋ, 61.6– 66.5 
<specimenCount box="[897,942,475,499]" pageId="10" pageNumber="219" type="female">♀♀</specimenCount>
